#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:2
msgid "反序列化"
msgstr "Deserialization"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Introduction"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:6
msgid ""
"序列化就是把对象转换成字节流，便于保存在内存、文件、数据库中；反序列化即逆过程，由字节流还原成对象。一般用于远程调用、通过网络将对象传输至远程服务器、存储对象到数据库或本地等待重用等场景中。Java中的"
" ``ObjectOutputStream`` 类的 ``writeObject()`` 方法可以实现序列化，类 "
"``ObjectInputStream`` 类的 ``readObject()`` 方法用于反序列化。如果要实现类的反序列化，则是对其实现 "
"``Serializable`` 接口。"
msgstr ""
"Serialization converts objects into byte streams so they can be stored in "
"memory, files, or databases. Deserialization is the reverse process, "
"restoring objects from byte streams. It is commonly used in scenarios such "
"as remote calls, transmitting objects to remote servers over the network, "
"and storing objects in a database or locally for later reuse. In Java, the "
"``writeObject()`` method of the ``ObjectOutputStream`` class implements "
"serialization, and the ``readObject()`` method of the ``ObjectInputStream`` "
"class is used for deserialization. To make a class deserializable, implement "
"the ``Serializable`` interface."

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:8
msgid "当远程服务接受不可信的数据并进行反序列化且当前环境中存在可利用的类时，就认为存在反序列化漏洞。"
msgstr "A deserialization vulnerability is considered present when a remote service accepts untrusted data, deserializes it, and the current environment contains exploitable classes."

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:11
msgid "序列数据结构"
msgstr "Serialized Data Structure"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:12
msgid "``0xaced`` 魔术头 / STREAM_MAGIC"
msgstr "``0xaced`` magic header / STREAM_MAGIC"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:13
msgid "``0x0005`` 版本号 / STREAM_VERSION / 参考 java.io.ObjectStreamConstants"
msgstr "``0x0005`` version number / STREAM_VERSION / see java.io.ObjectStreamConstants"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:14
msgid "``0x73`` 对象类型标识"
msgstr "``0x73`` object type identifier"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:15
msgid "``0x72`` 类描述符标识"
msgstr "``0x72`` class descriptor identifier"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:18
msgid "序列化流程"
msgstr "Serialization Flow"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:19
msgid "ObjectOutputStream实例初始化时，将魔术头和版本号写入bout (BlockDataOutputStream类型) 中"
msgstr "When an ObjectOutputStream instance is initialized, it writes the magic header and version number into bout, which is of type BlockDataOutputStream"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:20
msgid "调用ObjectOutputStream.writeObject()开始写对象数据"
msgstr "Call ObjectOutputStream.writeObject() to start writing object data"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:21
msgid ""
"ObjectStreamClass.lookup()封装待序列化的类描述 (返回ObjectStreamClass类型) "
"，获取包括类名、自定义serialVersionUID、可序列化字段 (返回ObjectStreamField类型) "
"和构造方法，以及writeObject、readObject方法等"
msgstr ""
"ObjectStreamClass.lookup() wraps the class description to be serialized, "
"returning an ObjectStreamClass. It obtains the class name, custom "
"serialVersionUID, serializable fields returned as ObjectStreamField, "
"constructors, and methods such as writeObject and readObject"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:22
msgid "writeOrdinaryObject()写入对象数据"
msgstr "writeOrdinaryObject() writes object data"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:23
msgid "写入对象类型标识"
msgstr "Write the object type identifier"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:24
msgid "writeClassDesc()进入分支writeNonProxyDesc()写入类描述数据"
msgstr "writeClassDesc() enters the writeNonProxyDesc() branch to write class description data"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:25
msgid "写入类描述符标识"
msgstr "Write the class descriptor identifier"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:26
msgid "写入类名"
msgstr "Write the class name"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:27
msgid "写入SUID (当SUID为空时，会进行计算并赋值)"
msgstr "Write the SUID; when the SUID is empty, it is calculated and assigned"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:28
msgid "计算并写入序列化属性标志位"
msgstr "Calculate and write the serialized property flags"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:29
msgid "写入字段信息数据"
msgstr "Write field information data"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:30
msgid "写入Block Data结束标识"
msgstr "Write the Block Data end marker"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:31
msgid "写入父类描述数据"
msgstr "Write parent class description data"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:32
msgid "writeSerialData()写入对象的序列化数据"
msgstr "writeSerialData() writes the object's serialized data"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:33
msgid ""
"若类自定义了writeObject()，则调用该方法写对象，否则调用defaultWriteFields()写入对象的字段数据 "
"(若是非原始类型，则递归处理子对象)"
msgstr ""
"If the class defines writeObject(), call that method to write the object; "
"otherwise call defaultWriteFields() to write the object's field data. For "
"non-primitive types, child objects are processed recursively"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:36
msgid "反序列化流程"
msgstr "Deserialization Flow"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:37
msgid "ObjectInputStream实例初始化时，读取魔术头和版本号进行校验"
msgstr "When an ObjectInputStream instance is initialized, it reads the magic header and version number for validation"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:38
msgid "调用ObjectInputStream.readObject()开始读对象数据"
msgstr "Call ObjectInputStream.readObject() to start reading object data"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:39
msgid "读取对象类型标识"
msgstr "Read the object type identifier"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:40
msgid "readOrdinaryObject()读取数据对象"
msgstr "readOrdinaryObject() reads the data object"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:41
msgid "readClassDesc()读取类描述数据"
msgstr "readClassDesc() reads class description data"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:42
msgid "读取类描述符标识，进入分支readNonProxyDesc()"
msgstr "Read the class descriptor identifier and enter the readNonProxyDesc() branch"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:43
msgid "读取类名"
msgstr "Read the class name"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:44
msgid "读取SUID"
msgstr "Read the SUID"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:45
msgid "读取并分解序列化属性标志位"
msgstr "Read and parse the serialized property flags"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:46
msgid "读取字段信息数据"
msgstr "Read field information data"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:47
msgid "resolveClass()根据类名获取待反序列化的类的Class对象，如果获取失败，则抛出ClassNotFoundException"
msgstr "resolveClass() obtains the Class object for the class to be deserialized by class name; if retrieval fails, it throws ClassNotFoundException"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:48
msgid "skipCustomData()循环读取字节直到Block Data结束标识为止"
msgstr "skipCustomData() loops through bytes until the Block Data end marker is reached"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:49
msgid "读取父类描述数据"
msgstr "Read parent class description data"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:50
msgid "initNonProxy()中判断对象与本地对象的SUID和类名 (不含包名) 是否相同，若不同，则抛出InvalidClassException"
msgstr "In initNonProxy(), determine whether the object's SUID and class name, excluding the package name, are the same as those of the local object; if they differ, throw InvalidClassException"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:51
msgid ""
"ObjectStreamClass.newInstance()获取并调用离对象最近的非Serializable的父类的无参构造方法 "
"(若不存在，则返回null) 创建对象实例"
msgstr ""
"ObjectStreamClass.newInstance() obtains and calls the no-argument "
"constructor of the nearest non-Serializable parent class of the object, or "
"returns null if it does not exist, to create an object instance"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:52
msgid "readSerialData()读取对象的序列化数据"
msgstr "readSerialData() reads the object's serialized data"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:53
msgid "若类自定义了readObject()，则调用该方法读对象，否则调用defaultReadFields()读取并填充对象的字段数据"
msgstr "If the class defines readObject(), call that method to read the object; otherwise call defaultReadFields() to read and populate the object's field data"

