msgstr "Hook resolveClass"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:90
msgid ""
"在使用 ``readObject()`` 反序列化时会调用 ``resolveClass`` "
"方法读取反序列化的类名，可以通过hook该方法来校验反序列化的类，一个Demo如下"
msgstr ""
"When ``readObject()`` is used for deserialization, the ``resolveClass`` "
"method is called to read the deserialized class name. This method can be "
"hooked to validate the deserialized class. A Demo is shown below"

#: ../../source/language/java/unserialize.rst:104
msgid ""
"以上的Demo就只允许序列化 ``SerialObject`` "
"，通过这种方式，就可以设置允许序列化的白名单，来防止反序列化漏洞被利用。SerialKiller/Jackson/Weblogic等都使用了这种方式来防御。"
msgstr "The Demo above allows only ``SerialObject`` to be serialized. In this way, a whitelist of classes allowed for serialization can be configured to prevent exploitation of deserialization vulnerabilities. SerialKiller, Jackson, WebLogic, and others use this approach for defense."

